            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>rectangles</strong> end to end and press together firmly so you end up with long piece[s]</p><p>Tip: Dab a little cold water on the edge to help them stick together!</p><p>Spoon the <strong>cheese</strong> <strong>filling </strong>into the centre of the pastry in an even line, then brush the long edge of the pastry with a little bit of <strong>cold water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
