      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomatoes</strong> roughly</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>remaining honey</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong>, then add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>cucumber</strong> and the <strong>salad</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
