    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, sprinkle your <strong>ground sumac</strong> and <strong>remaining toasted sesame seeds</strong> over the <strong>roast potatoes </strong>and mix everything together – these are your <strong>sumac & sesame roast potatoes</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>harissa & cheese spanakopita-style tart </strong>with the <strong>sumac & sesame roast potatoes</strong> and<strong> dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
